item.title: Richscape item id list
item.dc:creator: @Mattch Mattch
item.description:
@Mattch wrote:

When you open your richscape client (to play) another window also opens behind it, minimize your playing client to see the id list for richscape items

To see ids for items like black platelegs use the moparscape one as they work
